<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Seabe Pay | The WhatsApp CRM for Grooming Professionals</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800 font-sans antialiased">

    <section class="relative bg-gray-900 text-white overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black opacity-60 z-0"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-32 text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6">
                Unleash Your Craft. <span class="text-blue-500">Systemize Your Growth.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Stop letting scheduling chaos, manual client notes, and awkward payment queues hold your business back. Seabe Digital is the WhatsApp-native CRM and payment ecosystem built specifically for South Africa’s top personal grooming professionals.
            </p>
            <a href="#demo-form" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full text-lg transition duration-300 shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                Systemize My Shop Today
            </a>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-400 italic">Zero hardware costs. Zero monthly subscription fees. You only pay when you earn.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200 py-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-between items-center text-sm md:text-base font-semibold text-gray-600 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock text-blue-500 mr-2"></i> Bank-Grade Security</div>
            <div class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-green-500 mr-2"></i> 100% WhatsApp Native</div>
            <div class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-regular fa-credit-card text-blue-500 mr-2"></i> Capitec Pay, EFT & Card</div>
            <div class="flex items-center"><i class="fa-solid fa-earth-africa text-green-700 mr-2"></i> Built for the SA Economy</div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-red-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 text-red-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-900 mb-4">The Problem: You are an artisan, not an administrator.</h3>
                <p class="text-red-800 leading-relaxed">
                    Your talent is the craft. But as your business grows, the admin becomes a nightmare. Lost style notes, unconfirmed bookings, the high cost of no-shows, and manual cash counting at the end of a long day are stealing your time and eating your margins.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-blue-100 shadow-sm">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check-double"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Solution: Your Invisible Manager.</h3>
                <p class="text-blue-800 leading-relaxed">
                    We replace the messy paper diary and the clunky card machine with an invisible, digital manager that lives right inside your clients' favorite app: <strong>WhatsApp</strong>. Seamless booking, automatic records, and instant payments—all in one chat.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white py-20 border-t border-gray-100">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16 text-gray-900">How the Ecosystem Works</h2>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-wallet"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">1. The "Chair-Side" Checkout</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 italic">Never make a client queue at the front desk again.</p>
                    <ul class="text-left text-gray-600 space-y-2 text-sm">
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>Send payment links directly to their WhatsApp in the chair.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>Accept Card, Instant EFT, or Capitec Pay instantly.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>"Smart Tipping" prompts increase staff take-home by up to 20%.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">2. Seabe CRM: Digital Memory</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 italic">Treat every walk-in like a VIP regular.</p>
                    <ul class="text-left text-gray-600 space-y-2 text-sm">
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>Auto-log style notes, preferred barber, and purchase history.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>Ditch the scattered paper notebooks.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>Automated nudges: "Been 3 weeks since your fade. Book now?"</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl mx-auto mb-6 shadow-sm">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-ban"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">3. The "No-Show" Killer</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 italic">An empty chair is lost money.</p>
                    <ul class="text-left text-gray-600 space-y-2 text-sm">
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>Require a micro-deposit (e.g., R50) via Seabe Pay to book.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>Weed out uncommitted clients.</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-green-500 mr-2"></i>Protect your calendar and guarantee your daily revenue.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">The Master Ledger</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-blue-400 font-semibold mb-8">Built specifically for the Commission & Booth Rental Model</p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Are you managing multiple chairs? The Seabe Master Ledger automatically splits every transaction in real-time. 
                <br><br>
                <strong class="text-white">The Shop’s Cut</strong> routes to the main business account.<br>
                <strong class="text-white">The Stylist’s Commission</strong> routes instantly to their virtual wallet.
            </p>
            <div class="inline-block bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700 shadow-xl">
                <p class="text-lg font-bold text-green-400"><i class="fa-solid fa-scale-balanced mr-2"></i> Result: Zero manual recon at month-end. Total transparency.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="demo-form" class="bg-gray-50 py-24">
        <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8 border border-gray-100">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 text-center">Ready to Professionalize?</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-center mb-8">Request a secure demonstration of the Seabe Ecosystem.</p>
                
                <form action="/api/demo-request" method="POST" class="space-y-5">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Full Name</label>
                        <input type="text" name="fullName" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 outline-none transition">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Shop / Business Name</label>
                        <input type="text" name="shopName" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 outline-none transition">
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Business Type</label>
                            <select name="businessType" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 outline-none bg-white">
                                <option>Barbershop</option>
                                <option>Hair Salon</option>
                                <option>Nail Studio</option>
                                <option>Other</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Chairs/Stylists</label>
                            <select name="teamSize" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 outline-none bg-white">
                                <option>1 (Solo)</option>
                                <option>2 - 4</option>
                                <option>5+</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">WhatsApp Number</label>
                        <input type="tel" name="whatsappNumber" required placeholder="+27..." class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 outline-none transition">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-4 rounded-lg text-lg transition duration-300 shadow-md mt-4">
                        Request My Secure Demo
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-gray-950 text-gray-400 py-12 border-t border-gray-900">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-sm">
            <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0 text-center md:text-left">
                <p class="mb-2"><a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Terms of Service</a> | <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition">Contact Us</a></p>
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope mr-2"></i> madoda@seabe.co.za <span class="mx-2">|</span> <i class="fa-solid fa-phone mr-2"></i> +27 87 265 7872</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center md:text-right text-xs max-w-sm">
                <p>Disclaimer: Seabe Digital (Pty) Ltd operates as a registered Third-Party Payment Provider utilizing established South African banking infrastructure.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>